{"2083160":{"success":true,"data":{"type":"game","name":"Disfigure","steam_appid":2083160,"required_age":0,"is_free":true,"dlc":[2497100],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Disfigure is entirely free to play for the time being, so please consider supporting us through the donation DLC!<\/strong><\/p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay<\/h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In an arena shrouded by darkness, pay keen attention to your surroundings where monsters could be lurking. Choose between circle and cone vision: one allows you to see all around but not far, while the latter allows you to see far in one direction. Survive for as long as possible. <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/2083160\/extras\/combat.gif?t=1743042236\" \/><\/p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Variety of Builds<\/h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from over 150 upgrades and weapon perks to create a unique build for each run. Become a pyromaniac, shoot lightning, fire a storm of bullets, or even harness light to destroy your enemies! <\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/2083160\/extras\/lightning.gif?t=1743042236\" \/><\/p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Variety of Weapons<\/h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock new weapons with currency earned from runs! Each weapon behaves differently and has its own unique perks allowing for a multitude of different builds.<\/p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:\/\/shared.akamai.steamstatic.com\/store_item_assets\/steam\/apps\/2083160\/extras\/weaponselect.gif?t=1743042236\" \/><\/p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Content<\/h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">2 maps with 19 unique enemies and 6 bosses in total<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 150 unique upgrades to choose from<\/p><\/li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">15+ weapons each with uni